프로젝트 `D:\16. 자동화 도구\safeAutoTest`에서 작업합니다. Next.js App Router. 다음이 커밋돼 있습니다: `lib/site-manager.ts`, `lib/site-runner.ts`, `lib/site-run-progress.ts`, `lib/site-types.ts`.

**목표:** 3개 API 라우트 파일을 생성하고 커밋합니다.

**규칙:** 아래 3개 파일만 생성. 다른 파일 절대 수정 금지.

---

**`app/api/sites/[id]/storage-state/route.ts` 생성** (디렉터리 포함):

```ts
import fs from "node:fs";
import path from "node:path";
import { NextResponse } from "next/server";
import type { NextRequest } from "next/server";
import { getSite, saveSite } from "@/lib/site-manager";

export async function POST(req: NextRequest, { params }: { params: { id: string } }) {
  const site = getSite(params.id);
  if (!site) return NextResponse.json({ success: false, error: "Not found" }, { status: 404 });

  const body = await req.json();
  if (typeof body !== "object" || body === null) {
    return NextResponse.json({ success: false, error: "Invalid storageState" }, { status: 400 });
  }

  const dir = path.join(process.cwd(), "data", "sites", params.id);
  fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true });
  const target = path.join(dir, "storage-state.json");
  fs.writeFileSync(target, JSON.stringify(body, null, 2), "utf-8");

  saveSite({
    ...site,
    storageStatePath: path.relative(process.cwd(), target),
    updatedAt: new Date().toISOString(),
  });

  return NextResponse.json({ success: true });
}
```

**`app/api/sites/[id]/run/route.ts` 생성** (디렉터리 포함):

```ts
import { NextResponse } from "next/server";
import type { NextRequest } from "next/server";
import { getSite } from "@/lib/site-manager";
import { runSite } from "@/lib/site-runner";
import { setSiteRunProgress } from "@/lib/site-run-progress";

export async function POST(_: NextRequest, { params }: { params: { id: string } }) {
  const site = getSite(params.id);
  if (!site) return NextResponse.json({ success: false, error: "Not found" }, { status: 404 });

  try {
    const result = await runSite(site);
    return NextResponse.json({ success: true, data: result });
  } catch (error) {
    setSiteRunProgress({
      siteId: site.id, runId: "", status: "error",
      startedAt: new Date().toISOString(), updatedAt: new Date().toISOString(),
      visited: 0, total: 0,
      error: error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error),
    });
    return NextResponse.json(
      { success: false, error: error instanceof Error ? error.message : String(error) },
      { status: 500 }
    );
  }
}
```

**`app/api/sites/[id]/run-status/route.ts` 생성** (디렉터리 포함):

